                        <interp inst="t18600507-name-281" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>WILLIAM WEBSTER</persName>
                  </hi>. This half-crown is bad.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I did not know it was bad.</p>
